{"tid":1850922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［分析］香港有社區爆發機會大嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-29T19:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T20:13:38.000Z","uid":236080,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"487424cd6c99bdc36bbbf5234bd7303d3df3c3fb","tid":1850922,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:46:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>點解病毒喺武漢死亡率及傳染率高？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n因為佢地可能早係10月中左右已經開始爆發，人民衛生意識差再加上市政府隱瞞，導致大量人感染並且拖延治療，錯過最佳治療及防疫時間，導致宜家情況，所以死亡人士都係武漢人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>會經空氣傳播，香港人口密集咪避無可避</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係，今次同03年唔同嘅係香港人好快就全面提高個人衛生意識，戴口罩/用酒精搓手液，基本上全港80%人都每日戴口罩出街，而且宜家停課，部分公司在家工作，的確大大減低爆發風險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>中咗實死冇生？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n死者絕大部分甚至全部都係武漢/湖北人，錯過最佳治療時間，已經好難醫。反觀睇下：台灣，泰國，外國已經有患者好翻出院，所以唔洗擔心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>香港咁多大陸人湧落嚟係咪玩完？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n一定唔係！只要人人口罩，無論患者/健康都戴好口罩，勤用酒精搓手液，一定唔中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>洗唔洗買定糧食放屋企？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個糧食慌係因為啲人驚落街中招多過因為驚無糧食到港。買定適量嘅食物就得，宜家唔係打仗，斷水斷糧啊，唔好人買你又買。但口罩就好重要！買到就要買！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>要頂幾耐先完啊疫情</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n嚟近14-20日係關鍵期，如果0本地確診人數，依然只係輸入個案，香港疫情會穩定㗎喇，但當然唔可以鬆懈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>疫苗呢？解藥呢？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n無咁快，大陸口講最快都要一個月。正常最就要3個月至一年作測試。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>病毒係咪變種，唔怕熱，點解中東澳洲都有？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地都係輸入個案，都係去過武漢，而當地係冇本土傳染個案。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>香港點先安全？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊14-20日一過，就知香港疫情嚴唔嚴重。如果政府想港人可以經陸路口岸回港，可以關閉全部口岸，只開放一個口岸並只批准香港居民進入，再無港人在內地，就全面封關。人人戴口罩，出街都得，但要注意衛生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝大家身體健康 百毒不侵</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903a67b3f78dd0b7f55b804b5a79182ff08972b4","tid":1850922,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"計漏咗香港太多支那人"},{"pid":"1400c5ff9468e9555a6813f87f2ebd74f60302cf","tid":1850922,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:48:19.000Z","msg":"特別糧食慌，大家真係唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇停外國進口貨運<br />\n外國都冇話停止進口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48af3d76d7cbcc9093dc26203ba3a1a1f651f533","tid":1850922,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903a67b3f78dd0b7f55b804b5a79182ff08972b4","tid":1850922,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"計漏咗香港太多支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:49:15.000Z","msg":"支那人等14-20日都會原形畢露<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家日日口罩同衛生<br />\n<br />\n就唔怕架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac279f2049cc5c88dcb69ce9f905b7b459a1f460","tid":1850922,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T19:50:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41044edce156bead58ae99e0bf85c7b03035d203","tid":1850922,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1